<emphasis id="B94A0D150D15AEDBBA17CD5B103269E3" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="196">16:</emphasis>
Material aus dem Rednitztal (Deutschland) (Hofelich 1935).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C0CD96F3803617C019329CE56E2ECB7B" pageId="null" pageNumber="196">
<emphasis id="EC85C3A70E7B91623E90A20B2534F190" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="196">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin, montan und subalpin. 
<normalizedToken id="04A0D6D0EE2361543CD1EFAF75A09166" originalValue="Ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="196">Aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName id="01A598E550DF4888CEA696D7B0901D2D" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Plantaginaceae" genus="Veronica" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="196" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="verna">
<emphasis id="CA6E487BFC5070C32800277CAAB59CE6" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="196">V. verna</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 15b). 
<emphasis id="F809141C5CB42233F1D3C58A7651B1B9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="196">Stipo-Poion xerophilae</emphasis>
Br.-Bl. et Tx. 1943, 
<emphasis id="66ADA59F660539E04032C7278232559B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="196">Sedo-Scleranthion</emphasis>
Br.-Bl. 1949.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5625C20A2502FDE5C1D6AF775CD59148" pageId="null" pageNumber="196">
<emphasis id="FF688373D6D6D8A47F5EBF6063F4D2F0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="196">
